title: Can I still transfer messages from Pixel 2 to 5 even after initial setup was interrupted?
content: When I connected old pixel 2 to 5 for initial data transfer, they battery was drained on the 2 within minutes. And the setup was interrupted. Messages did not get through at all. Any chance I can still transfer them somehow, or are they lost?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 5
